snippet.title: Whispike Survivors: Sword of the Necromancer - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cultivate the strongest monster in this horde survivor farming game! Fight against waves of creatures to beef up your Whispike and use its seeds to create even stronger hybrids!

Whispike Survivors will be available for PC, PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series and Nintendo Switch very soon. Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2348280/Whispike_Survivors__Sword_of_the_Necromancer/
